c: 27
v: 88
t: "Ni tinchigaonaga matumbi ni kugaganichisyaga kuti gali chilimbanganile (m’malo mwakwe), nambo kutendaga gali nkwenda mugakwendelaga mawunde gawula. (Gele) nimasengo ga Allah Ajula jwaachikolosisye chenene chindu chilichose. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Nkusimanya chenene abali syosope sya yankutenda"